Charlet Chung https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlet_Chung 0 Charlet Chung (born 16 February 1983) is an American actress who trained at the University of California, San Diego. Her first acting role was Barbie Yen in the twentieth episode of the third season of the American police procedural television series Cold Case and is also known for voice acting as D.Va in the video game Overwatch.
